item.title: How do I make a new home
item.dc:creator: @James-RevolutionX James-RevolutionX
item.description:
@James-RevolutionX wrote:

Teleport home & DONT MOVE then do ::mypos, use those coordinates and teleport to varrock and then find where you want to be teleported to and do ::mypos, then go into clickingmost.java and type in the old coords ( edgeville home coords ) and change them with your new ones from ( varrock ), you might want to move objects before changing home teleports.

item.dc:creator: @runefreak10 runefreak10
item.description:
@runefreak10 wrote:

Look for the teleport command that takes you to edgeville and simply change the coordinates in it… Of course you’re going to have the side stuff like moving/deleting objects, npcs, etc. from your old home unless you don’t want to.
